    RefIds:
    - rid: 107151340257149004
      type: {class: WeighedChoice, ns: , asm: Assembly-CSharp}
      data:
        modules:
        - weight: 25
          module:
          - rid: 107151343762276430
          output: 'The bravery of our people is commendable. They charged into the
            roaring flames and, by the grace of the Beholder, rescued those trapped
            inside. Not only that, but they managed to douse the fire entirely. The
            laborers are now lining up to join our sect. The Beholder smiles upon
            us!

            [Gained 30 Flock]'
        - weight: 50
          module:
          - rid: 107151343762276431
          output: 'Our men managed to extinguish the flames, yet none dared to venture
            into the burning structure until it was far too late. The poor souls
            trapped within are now with the Beholder. Even so, the Overseer offered
            a reward for the service rendered.

            [Gained 10 Wealth]'
        - weight: 25
          module:
          - rid: 107151343762276432
          - rid: 107151343762276433
          output: 'What a tragedy! Our brave followers entered the inferno without
            fear in their hearts to save the trapped men. But as time passed, it
            became clear that no one was coming out. May the Beholder gently receive
            our valiant martyrs.

            [Gained 10 Zeal Lost 10 Bliss]'
